Package com.google.publicalerts.cap.feed

This package contains classes to parse and write feeds (Atom, RSS, and more) enclosing CAP messages.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CapFeedParser
    Parses feeds of alerts, the entries in those feeds, and the CAP alerts in those entries.
    CapFeedParser.DocBuilder
    Pulled out of Rome to take advantage of their XEE prevention
    CapFeedValidator
    Validates portions of Atom/RSS feeds (fat or thin) of CAP alerts beyond what is done in by the schemas in CapFeedParser.
    SimpleFatCapAtomFeedBuilder
    Writes one or more Alerts in XML format to an Atom feed.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    CapFeedException
    An exception for CAP feeds.

Package com.google.publicalerts.cap.feed Description

This package contains classes to parse and write feeds (Atom, RSS, and more) enclosing CAP messages. Currently Atom and RSS are supported.
